Class IOGenerator

java.lang.Object
  ibis.compile.IbiscComponent
      ibis.io.rewriter.IOGenerator

public class IOGenerator
extends ibis.compile.IbiscComponent

The IOGenerator is responsible for collecting the classes to be rewritten and rewriting them in the proper order.
